{"tid":1536842,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【反修例】調查元朗襲擊3個動議　元朗區議會全部否決","createTime":"2019-09-03T17:32:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T17:35:38.000Z","uid":76368,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bb2dafb8a109f65a89ed2dfde1f154057dddbe90","tid":1536842,"uid":76368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:32:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2443359\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2443359&d=KYuNOZm%2F4ip93LesI4%2B6voL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=339febab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2443359</a><br />\n<br />\n元朗西鐵站7月21日晚上發生白衣人無差別襲擊事件，造成45人受傷。元朗區議會於今（3日）合併討論721元朗暴力襲擊事件，其中有議員動議要求成立獨立調查委員會，惟遭過半數議員反對，3個有關調查721元朗無差別襲擊案的動議均遭否決。<br />\n<br />\n元朗區議會黃偉賢議員就元朗721無差別襲擊事件，在會議上動議要求成立獨立調查委員會，其中包括支持監警會徹查各界對警察的各項指責及成立對話平台等。議案最終以7票贊成、22票反對、2票棄權否決有關動議。<br />\n<br />\n其中贊成的議員包括：陳美蓮、杜嘉倫、黃偉賢、麥業成、李月民、鄺俊宇以及湛家雄；而反對的議員則包括鄧家良、楊家安、袁敏兒、梁明堅、鄧慶業、鄧卓然、蕭浪鳴、陸頌雄、鄧焯謙、姚國威、劉桂容、文美桂、文家駒、黃煒玲、馬淑燕、呂堅、梁福元、梁志祥、鄧鎔耀、郭強、趙秀嫻及程振明；陳思靜及王威信表示棄權。<br />\n<br />\n而李月民議員動議要求成立「檢討721元朗西鐵站暴力事件」的工作小組，議案最終以8票贊成、20票反對、3票棄權否決有關動議。<br />\n<br />\n其後，黃偉賢議員針對元朗白衣人無差別襲擊市民，再次動議成立檢討小組，最終以5票贊成、22票反對、2票棄權，再次否決動議。"},{"pid":"ab6d4d62d26390a7aef08ab87f19ab97ab9b0be4","tid":1536842,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:32:15.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abea43938e9d8ae6913f9322dbbe710b74c4b920","tid":1536842,"uid":248166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:34:00.000Z","msg":"應承咗你幫你推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f40146d0117e53a39d9cec6bcc52bd5a0ad0905","tid":1536842,"uid":244034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:34:07.000Z","msg":"根本成班鄕黑係區議會點會查"},{"pid":"6bffdf256eb184f83cb5e7e105a2826885e4d787","tid":1536842,"uid":2607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:34:51.000Z","msg":"王威信有份做架屌你"},{"pid":"5304259dd91c5f22d73198ee3b3c61af6c7bcf83","tid":1536842,"uid":221490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:35:38.000Z","msg":"同警監會查警察有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}